---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Book — From Problem Solving to Solution Design"
  description="Order 'From Problem Solving to Solution Design: Turning Ideas into Actions' by J. Eduardo Campos and Erica W. Campos."
>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="book-content">
        <h1>From Problem Solving to Solution Design</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Turning Ideas into Actions</p>
        <p>
          This book is a field guide to finding the best path when designing sustainable solutions
          for complex problems within organizations. It provides five critical checkpoints to aid
          those designing and implementing solutions, as well as many innovative techniques and
          resources.
        </p>
        <p>
          J. Eduardo Campos and Erica W. Campos share over fifty years of combined formal
          training, research, and solution-designing experience addressing both everyday situations
          and complex organizational problems.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://amzn.to/4akqZ3n"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn-primary"
          aria-label="Order the book on Amazon"
        >Order on Amazon</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .book-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
